>>LISA: It's an education.

00:33:23.893 --> 00:33:25.060 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: And it's dignity.

00:33:25.060 --> 00:33:27.410 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And it's dignity,
is what it really is.

00:33:27.410 --> 00:33:28.210 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:33:28.210 --> 00:33:31.150 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And it's re-educating
an entire generation.

00:33:31.150 --> 00:33:32.680 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Oh, yeah.

00:33:32.680 --> 00:33:34.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And so on.

00:33:34.030 --> 00:33:38.110 align:middle line:84%
And now there are statistics
that we hear of all the time,

00:33:38.110 --> 00:33:43.690 align:middle line:84%
55% of women in the region of
Africa are attending school.

00:33:43.690 --> 00:33:45.820 align:middle line:84%
There's these
statistics, but they grow

00:33:45.820 --> 00:33:47.950 align:middle line:84%
and they change
every single day.

00:33:47.950 --> 00:33:49.790 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: They do, they do.

00:33:49.790 --> 00:33:55.450 align:middle line:10%
And especially when you
focus and educate more girls,

00:33:55.450 --> 00:33:58.450 align:middle line:10%
you change the whole generation.

00:33:58.450 --> 00:34:01.000 align:middle line:90%
There's power in that.

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:02.920 align:middle line:84%
In our schools, they
are public schools,

00:34:02.920 --> 00:34:05.260 align:middle line:90%
we educate both boys and girls.

00:34:05.260 --> 00:34:07.600 align:middle line:84%
But what has been
fascinating for me

00:34:07.600 --> 00:34:12.590 align:middle line:84%
is to see girls
outperforming boys.

00:34:12.590 --> 00:34:15.760 align:middle line:84%
And I am-- and they
are so determined.

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:16.870 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Like you were.

00:34:16.870 --> 00:34:17.670 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yes.

00:34:17.670 --> 00:34:21.250 align:middle line:84%
I think it's because, also,
they see me in the community.

00:34:21.250 --> 00:34:25.030 align:middle line:84%
At least they can see a
role model and they can say,

00:34:25.030 --> 00:34:27.380 align:middle line:90%
I want to be just like her.

00:34:27.380 --> 00:34:33.159 align:middle line:84%
And I've seen older men coming,
holding their eight-year-old

00:34:33.159 --> 00:34:37.360 align:middle line:84%
daughters and looking into
my eyes and say, Tererai,

00:34:37.360 --> 00:34:39.520 align:middle line:90%
can she be just like you?

00:34:39.520 --> 00:34:43.929 align:middle line:84%
And I realize in those moments
that not only are we providing

00:34:43.929 --> 00:34:47.320 align:middle line:84%
quality education, but we
are helping communities

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:53.560 align:middle line:84%
to transform in seeing the
importance of educating girls

00:34:53.560 --> 00:34:54.460 align:middle line:90%
as well.

00:34:54.460 --> 00:34:56.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, and
to break the cycle.

00:34:56.300 --> 00:34:57.100 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Exactly.

00:34:57.100 --> 00:34:58.640 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That they don't
want for their daughters.

00:34:58.640 --> 00:34:59.800 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: No.

00:34:59.800 --> 00:35:04.220 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Now can I ask you
your personal practice?

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:07.720 align:middle line:84%
Do you find
inspiration every day?

00:35:07.720 --> 00:35:08.960 align:middle line:90%
Do you meditate?

00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:09.760 align:middle line:90%
Do you--

00:35:09.760 --> 00:35:10.590 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Oh.

00:35:10.590 --> 00:35:11.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --pray?

00:35:11.500 --> 00:35:12.300 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:13.420 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Visualize?

00:35:13.420 --> 00:35:17.170 align:middle line:84%
>>TERERAI: Every day,
because I grew up

00:35:17.170 --> 00:35:20.170 align:middle line:84%
with a grandmother who
said it's important for you

00:35:20.170 --> 00:35:27.040 align:middle line:84%
to own your own rituals,
because rituals, they ground us.

00:35:27.040 --> 00:35:32.260 align:middle line:84%
They provide that space
to grow our faith.

00:35:32.260 --> 00:35:37.450 align:middle line:84%
So every day, 4:00
AM, I have to be up

00:35:37.450 --> 00:35:40.540 align:middle line:84%
and I do what I
call fierce writing.

00:35:40.540 --> 00:35:47.410 align:middle line:84%
I write and I write anything
that comes to my mind.

00:35:47.410 --> 00:35:54.760 align:middle line:84%
And I'm finding it is in those
hours where I am more creative.

00:35:54.760 --> 00:35:58.330 align:middle line:90%
I visualize every day.

00:35:58.330 --> 00:36:01.450 align:middle line:84%
When I buried my
dreams, my grandmother

00:36:01.450 --> 00:36:05.320 align:middle line:84%
would say go to that place where
you have buried your dreams,

00:36:05.320 --> 00:36:10.600 align:middle line:84%
sit still, visualize as
though you're already

00:36:10.600 --> 00:36:12.500 align:middle line:90%
living that life.

00:36:12.500 --> 00:36:16.120 align:middle line:84%
And I would visualize myself
getting into an aeroplane,

00:36:16.120 --> 00:36:17.440 align:middle line:90%
coming to America.

00:36:17.440 --> 00:36:20.980 align:middle line:10%
I'd never seen an aeroplane,
I'd never been in an aeroplane.

00:36:20.980 --> 00:36:25.120 align:middle line:84%
The only aeroplane that I
knew were war helicopters

00:36:25.120 --> 00:36:27.180 align:middle line:84%
that would come into
the communities.

00:36:27.180 --> 00:36:33.460 align:middle line:84%
So I would find myself
sitting into that helicopter.

00:36:33.460 --> 00:36:36.450 align:middle line:84%
It would take me to this
place called America.

00:36:36.450 --> 00:36:39.940 align:middle line:84%
And I would visualize
these tall buildings

00:36:39.940 --> 00:36:46.240 align:middle line:84%
and see myself carrying
books and attending classes.

00:36:46.240 --> 00:36:50.550 align:middle line:84%
Visualize getting my
undergraduate, my master's,

00:36:50.550 --> 00:36:51.880 align:middle line:90%
and my PhD.

00:36:51.880 --> 00:36:55.770 align:middle line:84%
Visualize going back,
building schools.

00:36:55.770 --> 00:36:58.660 align:middle line:84%
Visualize little girls
attending schools

00:36:58.660 --> 00:37:02.110 align:middle line:90%
and gaining their education.

00:37:02.110 --> 00:37:04.810 align:middle line:84%
The day that I went
into that aeroplane,

00:37:04.810 --> 00:37:09.010 align:middle line:84%
there was this deja vu feeling
that I've been here before.

00:37:09.010 --> 00:37:15.220 align:middle line:84%
So the power of daily rituals
is important in my life.

00:37:15.220 --> 00:37:20.450 align:middle line:84%
I talk about rituals, I
breathe rituals, I am rituals.

00:37:20.450 --> 00:37:25.580 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: They are so important,
and a lost art here.

00:37:25.580 --> 00:37:28.480 align:middle line:90%
And thank you for reminding us.

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:33.530 align:middle line:84%
Now do you visualize going back
to your community and teaching?

00:37:33.530 --> 00:37:36.580 align:middle line:90%
Do you visualize new dreams now?

00:37:36.580 --> 00:37:37.990 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: I live in Zimbabwe.

00:37:37.990 --> 00:37:41.650 align:middle line:84%
I had lived in this
country for almost 20 years

00:37:41.650 --> 00:37:44.950 align:middle line:84%
and relocated back
to my country.

00:37:44.950 --> 00:37:48.450 align:middle line:84%
I work in the communities
and I am in Zimbabwe--

00:37:48.450 --> 00:37:49.870 align:middle line:90%
I just came here yesterday.

00:37:49.870 --> 00:37:50.710 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:37:50.710 --> 00:37:51.550 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yes.

00:37:51.550 --> 00:37:53.230 align:middle line:90%
What is now my next dream?

00:37:53.230 --> 00:37:57.790 align:middle line:90%


00:37:57.790 --> 00:38:06.730 align:middle line:84%
I am burying my
dreams in your hearts.

00:38:06.730 --> 00:38:15.340 align:middle line:84%
I bury my dreams in the women
that I come across in my life.

00:38:15.340 --> 00:38:20.170 align:middle line:90%
I'm tired of digging the ground.

00:38:20.170 --> 00:38:25.735 align:middle line:84%
If I can bury my dreams in
your dreams, in your hearts--

00:38:25.735 --> 00:38:26.860 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It will grow roots.

00:38:26.860 --> 00:38:27.910 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: It will grow roots.

00:38:27.910 --> 00:38:28.710 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:38:28.710 --> 00:38:31.510 align:middle line:84%
>>TERERAI: And these are
not my personal dreams

00:38:31.510 --> 00:38:34.270 align:middle line:90%
that I am bearing.

00:38:34.270 --> 00:38:40.940 align:middle line:84%
I am bearing the awakening of
women, the awakening of women,

00:38:40.940 --> 00:38:44.975 align:middle line:84%
because we hold the power to
the healing of this world.

00:38:44.975 --> 00:38:48.750 align:middle line:90%


00:38:48.750 --> 00:38:52.035 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You just dug that
dream so deeply in my heart.

00:38:52.035 --> 00:38:52.910 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Thank you.

00:38:52.910 --> 00:38:55.630 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And in the hearts
of everyone watching.

00:38:55.630 --> 00:38:56.430 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:38:56.430 --> 00:38:57.300 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:38:57.300 --> 00:38:59.610 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That is exactly
what you're doing.

00:38:59.610 --> 00:39:03.210 align:middle line:84%
With every word you speak
and every story you tell,

00:39:03.210 --> 00:39:06.015 align:middle line:84%
you're weaving that
dream into our hearts.

00:39:06.015 --> 00:39:07.050 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah, yeah.

00:39:07.050 --> 00:39:09.060 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And we
will continue that.

