why she repeated the patterns

00:42:22.860 --> 00:42:24.100 align:middle line:90%
from her mother.

00:42:24.100 --> 00:42:24.900 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:42:24.900 --> 00:42:27.600 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And why her mother
repeated those patterns

00:42:27.600 --> 00:42:28.410 align:middle line:90%
from her mother.

00:42:28.410 --> 00:42:29.190 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:42:29.190 --> 00:42:30.750 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And as I'm
going through this--

00:42:30.750 --> 00:42:32.208 align:middle line:84%
you know, one would
think that this

00:42:32.208 --> 00:42:36.120 align:middle line:84%
is a time of grieving, but it's
a time of massive expansion

00:42:36.120 --> 00:42:39.970 align:middle line:90%
and learning the generations.

00:42:39.970 --> 00:42:41.250 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Yeah.

00:42:41.250 --> 00:42:42.510 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And then I look for--

00:42:42.510 --> 00:42:46.290 align:middle line:84%
I look at my daughter, and
