00:42:46.290 --> 00:42:48.617 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: The same pattern.

00:42:48.617 --> 00:42:50.325 align:middle line:84%
Because when you look
at those patterns--

00:42:50.325 --> 00:42:50.700 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:42:50.700 --> 00:42:51.410 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:42:51.410 --> 00:42:52.215 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: They have shaped us.

00:42:52.215 --> 00:42:52.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: They are deep.

00:42:52.930 --> 00:42:53.570 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: They are deep.

