>>TERERAI: Yes, yes.

00:43:36.900 --> 00:43:38.340 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Misconstrued as love.

00:43:38.340 --> 00:43:40.410 align:middle line:90%
>>TERERAI: Exactly, exactly.

00:43:40.410 --> 00:43:41.250 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

